<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students might use a variety of representations depending on the context, problem, or numbers.</p>
<ol>
      <li>$63</li>
      <li><ul>
<li>73 minutes</li>
<li>11:22 p.m.</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><ul>
<li>13 liters</li>
<li>550 kilograms</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li>6 ears of corn</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


